<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<chapter xml:id="chapter5-intro" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title><em>ISCAM</em> Chapter 5 Intro</title>

  <introduction>
    <p>The idea of comparisons has been a recurring theme throughout this course. In previous chapters, you were limited to exploring only one or two groups at a time. In this chapter, you extend those ideas to multiple groups and to relationships between variables.</p>
  </introduction>

